data.description: Convenient Woodland location on ½ acre lot!  This cute home features one level living, just outside of town, and close to amenities!  Upon entering your new home, you will notice and appreciate the open concept, natural light, three large bedrooms and TWO full bathrooms.  The oversized kitchen offers ample space for family meals, baking, and entertaining.  Off of the kitchen/dining area is a private backyard - a fantastic spot to enjoy outdoor time with friends and family or relaxing on your own. You have found your PLACE!
